User: Wait, there's a space after "f" in one link, like "17gWfRnHBfAOJdR2TAdWvUTWJ KUI2." That might be a copying error, as file IDs are usually continuous.

Grok: The standard Google Drive file link is https://drive.google.com/file/d/FILE_ID/view?. File IDs are typically 33 characters, like 1abc234567890abcde1234567890abcde.
